We act for Astro Entertainment Sdn. Bhd.,  
Technology Park Malaysia, Bukit Jalil, 57000 Kuala Lumpur (“our client”).  
Our client is Malaysia’s leading cross-media group   with significant  
presence in DTH (Direct-To-Home) TV services, commercial radio and TV  
programming. Astro is the brand name of the Malaysian direct broadcast  
satellite pay television service.

The blog page infringes our client’s copyright program, "Maharajalawak" as  
it uses to promote his/her blog by providing the downloadable links from  
another host web of the mentioned program.
